longBusinessSummary: Jericho Energy Ventures Inc. invests in hydrogen technologies, energy storage, carbon capture, and new energy systems. The company was formerly known as Jericho Oil Corporation and changed its name to Jericho Energy Ventures Inc. in March 2021. Jericho Energy Ventures Inc. was incorporated in 2010 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
